{"id":4174215,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"陈玺月是中国内地的女性配音演员。毕业于浙江传媒学院。2019年，荣获中国西部动漫文化节首届配音大赛特等奖。2022年，加入瞬心文化。","name":"陈玺月","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Xiyue Chen","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Xiyue Chen","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"陳璽月是中國內地的女性配音演員。畢業於浙江傳媒學院。2019 年，榮獲中國西部動漫文化節首屆配音大賽特等獎。2022 年，加入瞬心文化。","name":"陳璽月","primary":false}}]}